1
00:01:45,710 --> 00:01:48,590
Screw that little rabbit...

2
00:01:51,420 --> 00:01:53,300
Let's go, jinni !

3
00:01:55,790 --> 00:01:59,810
Did you call for me, Master?!

4
00:01:59,810 --> 00:02:03,610
That little rabbit...
I'm gonna chop her up!

5
00:02:05,600 --> 00:02:07,070
Time to show you

6
00:02:07,070 --> 00:02:09,780
what we can do!

7
00:02:19,740 --> 00:02:23,540
Minister Daifuku!
You're putting us in danger!

8
00:02:24,410 --> 00:02:27,710
What are you aiming at, jinni-san ?

9
00:02:29,330 --> 00:02:30,510
I won't let you get away!

10
00:02:30,510 --> 00:02:31,930
Come this way!

11
00:02:37,090 --> 00:02:39,020
How annoying!

12
00:02:39,020 --> 00:02:41,270
Jinn-uinely Enraged Cleave!

13
00:02:43,720 --> 00:02:46,860
Please stop, Minister Daifuku!

14
00:02:46,860 --> 00:02:48,400
That little...!

15
00:02:50,560 --> 00:02:53,740
That rat! She stole another helm!

16
00:02:53,740 --> 00:02:56,910
That crafty little rabbit!

17
00:03:01,530 --> 00:03:05,580
She's jumping from ship to ship
and making them attack each other!

18
00:03:05,580 --> 00:03:07,920
She sure is something...

19
00:03:07,920 --> 00:03:11,970
Yeah! She's awesome, right?!
She's like a little sister to me!

20
00:03:11,970 --> 00:03:15,980
When the moon cycle and the weather
are in their favor,

21
00:03:15,980 --> 00:03:18,560
the minks are quite strong.

22
00:03:18,560 --> 00:03:20,930
The moon cycle and the weather?

23
00:03:20,930 --> 00:03:23,100
Mm-hm...

24
00:03:23,100 --> 00:03:29,990
It is said that when the minks gaze
at a full moon on a clear night,

25
00:03:29,990 --> 00:03:36,040
their feral instincts are awakened
from the depths of their memories.

26
00:03:36,040 --> 00:03:39,950
That white, beastly form is known as...

27
00:03:39,950 --> 00:03:43,830
the moon lion, Sulong!

28
00:03:43,830 --> 00:03:45,120
Sulong?!

29
00:03:45,120 --> 00:03:48,460
Originally, the transformation
made them lose their minds

30
00:03:48,460 --> 00:03:52,830
and attack everyone in sight,
so it was quite troublesome...

31
00:03:52,830 --> 00:03:56,750
both for others and themselves.

32
00:03:56,750 --> 00:04:00,430
For themselves?
What do you mean by that?

33
00:04:00,430 --> 00:04:06,480
If a mink is unable to control it,
they will get exhausted after a single night...

34
00:04:07,260 --> 00:04:08,630
and die.

35
00:04:08,630 --> 00:04:09,640
What?!

36
00:04:09,640 --> 00:04:10,860
Die?!

37
00:04:10,860 --> 00:04:16,700
So it's a double-edged sword...
It's a combat technique that could cost them their life.

38
00:04:17,900 --> 00:04:23,120
Carrot-san... stealing the enemy helms
is truly a genius strategy.

39
00:04:25,690 --> 00:04:31,090
With that in mind, I will provide assistance
until we are close enough to fight, too!

40
00:04:31,090 --> 00:04:32,530
Provide assistance?

41
00:04:32,530 --> 00:04:34,470
Won't you fall into the sea?!

42
00:04:35,660 --> 00:04:38,680
Don't worry about me...

43
00:04:45,010 --> 00:04:46,480
That's right!

44
00:04:46,480 --> 00:04:49,900
He can run on water...
because he's so light!

45
00:04:53,010 --> 00:04:58,520
Let's have those two secure our escape route,
and we'll keep moving forward at full speed!

46
00:04:58,520 --> 00:04:59,680
– Yeah!
– Mm-hm!

47
00:04:59,680 --> 00:05:02,450
Stop right there!

48
00:05:13,610 --> 00:05:15,610
Dodge to the left!

49
00:05:16,320 --> 00:05:18,200
To the right!

50
00:05:21,450 --> 00:05:24,870
Sluggie-gie!

51
00:05:44,370 --> 00:05:46,930
Prometheus...

52
00:05:47,660 --> 00:05:49,980
Zeus...

53
00:05:49,980 --> 00:05:51,680
Mama?

54
00:05:52,740 --> 00:05:54,780
Brother Peros!

55
00:05:54,780 --> 00:05:56,330
Mama's acting strange!

56
00:05:56,330 --> 00:05:59,510
Lick. Yeah, I know!

57
00:05:59,510 --> 00:06:02,490
She's getting skinnier
and is having a hard time breathing!

58
00:06:06,570 --> 00:06:10,990
Prometheus... Zeus...

59
00:06:10,990 --> 00:06:15,080
Napoleon! What happened
to Zeus and Prometheus?!

60
00:06:15,080 --> 00:06:16,880
I'm calling them over now!

61
00:06:16,880 --> 00:06:22,130
It's been almost eight hours
since she started on her ravenous rampage!

62
00:06:22,470 --> 00:06:26,580
We've never had a problem
stopping them before,

63
00:06:26,580 --> 00:06:29,620
and I've never seen Mama this hungry.

64
00:06:31,220 --> 00:06:37,910
Even we have no idea
what will happen to Mama.

65
00:06:37,910 --> 00:06:42,660
She's truly an unknown monster now. Lick.

66
00:06:42,660 --> 00:06:46,540
Will she make it to Cacao Island?

67
00:06:46,540 --> 00:06:49,310
By the way, Brother Peros,

68
00:06:49,310 --> 00:06:54,420
A report came in, saying that Pudding is
currently transporting the cake this way on a ship!

69
00:06:54,420 --> 00:06:58,550
Oh, really?!
She's our guardian angel!

70
00:06:58,550 --> 00:07:02,200
Well, there's a problem, Big Brother!

71
00:07:02,200 --> 00:07:06,270
It's true that Pudding
is coming with the cake...

72
00:07:06,270 --> 00:07:09,650
but the ship is... Bege's, apparently...

73
00:07:10,180 --> 00:07:12,900
Lick? Did you say Bege?!

74
00:07:12,900 --> 00:07:18,550
Why is the cake that's going to save this country
on that assassin's ship?!

75
00:07:18,550 --> 00:07:20,150
I-I don't know!

76
00:07:20,150 --> 00:07:22,950
What do you mean you don't know?!

77
00:07:22,950 --> 00:07:24,540
What are we gonna do now?!

78
00:07:24,540 --> 00:07:29,540
We can't trust that cake anymore!

79
00:07:49,180 --> 00:07:51,390
What are you doing, Black Leg?!

80
00:07:51,390 --> 00:07:54,500
That's what I should be saying!
Screw you!

81
00:07:54,500 --> 00:07:59,440
I will absolutely not
let you poison the cake!

82
00:07:59,440 --> 00:08:03,800
This cake will definitely
reach Big Mom's mouth, right?!

83
00:08:03,800 --> 00:08:09,110
Knowing that, what kind of idiot
wouldn't add in poison or explosives?

84
00:08:09,110 --> 00:08:12,720
This is our opportunity to take out
one of the Four Emperors!

85
00:08:12,720 --> 00:08:16,250
Do you realize how big of an opportunity
this is right now?!

86
00:08:16,250 --> 00:08:20,900
Shut up! This is a battle
with a cook's pride on the line!

87
00:08:20,900 --> 00:08:24,710
Don't interfere!
The taste alone will take care of our enemy!

88
00:08:24,710 --> 00:08:27,340
Huh?! Stop dreaming!

89
00:08:27,340 --> 00:08:32,910
Big Mom is a woman who has eaten tons of delicious
snacks from around the world in her lifetime,

90
00:08:32,910 --> 00:08:36,640
and you think you can make a cake
that will surpass her wildest imagination?!

91
00:08:37,340 --> 00:08:38,980
That's impossible!

92
00:08:38,980 --> 00:08:44,110
You're right! If that cake isn't good enough,
then we're done for!

93
00:08:44,110 --> 00:08:46,230
But I'll take you up on that bet!

94
00:08:46,230 --> 00:08:51,080
Even if we do succeed,
they won't let us leave alive!

95
00:08:51,080 --> 00:08:53,090
Cut the crap!

96
00:08:53,090 --> 00:08:57,680
I guess you don't know Big Mom's history!

97
00:08:57,680 --> 00:09:03,200
Mark my words, we will regret
not killing her when we had the chance!

98
00:09:14,760 --> 00:09:16,440
Father!

99
00:09:16,440 --> 00:09:18,800
What did you do to Father?!

100
00:09:18,800 --> 00:09:20,020
Black Leg!

101
00:09:20,020 --> 00:09:23,940
What did you make Father eat?!

102
00:09:23,940 --> 00:09:25,890
Ask him that.

103
00:09:28,210 --> 00:09:32,140
This cream... it's so good that
I could go to heaven right now.

104
00:09:32,140 --> 00:09:35,770
What?! He's about to die
from the deliciousness?!

105
00:09:35,770 --> 00:09:38,020
Father, thank goodness-rero !

106
00:09:38,020 --> 00:09:40,670
Listen to me, Bege...

107
00:09:42,860 --> 00:09:46,550
You're free to try
and assassinate her if you want...

108
00:09:46,550 --> 00:09:52,140
but... you can do it after
I have filled the stomach of my guest!

109
00:09:52,140 --> 00:09:57,480
I will feed anyone who wants to eat!
That is the job of a cook!

110
00:10:02,800 --> 00:10:04,000
Madam Pudding!

111
00:10:04,000 --> 00:10:05,900
Why are you collapsing?!

112
00:10:05,900 --> 00:10:11,140
Bege! It's been a while,
but even I helped with this!

113
00:10:11,140 --> 00:10:13,950
Believe in the power of sweets!

114
00:10:13,950 --> 00:10:19,380
Oh, damn...
It's like I've been hypnotized!

115
00:10:20,630 --> 00:10:25,050
Maybe this cake will work on Big Mom, too...

116
00:10:25,050 --> 00:10:28,020
Yeah... Okay...

117
00:10:29,350 --> 00:10:32,820
Now, let's hurry up!
Have you finished coating the cake?!

118
00:10:32,820 --> 00:10:34,740
Just a little more to go!

119
00:10:36,450 --> 00:10:40,540
Madam Chiffon!
Two of the cooks have fallen to the sweet smell!

120
00:10:40,540 --> 00:10:43,840
Guys! Get a hold of yourselves
until it's finished!

121
00:10:43,840 --> 00:10:45,090
Yes, madam!

122
00:10:46,320 --> 00:10:51,710
Stay safe, Nami-san,
I'm on my way!

123
00:10:52,610 --> 00:10:57,830
Hurry up! Hurry up!

124
00:10:57,830 --> 00:10:58,880
Which way?

125
00:10:58,880 --> 00:11:00,230
Straight ahead!

126
00:11:00,230 --> 00:11:02,920
I can feel Napoleon's presence!

127
00:11:02,920 --> 00:11:08,150
This is your fault, Prometheus.
You went back to eat the forest fire!

128
00:11:08,150 --> 00:11:12,390
Who's the one that caused me
so much harm, Zeus?!

129
00:11:12,930 --> 00:11:16,920
I can't believe you let yourself
be used by the enemy!

130
00:11:16,930 --> 00:11:22,510
We are special homies that were born
straight from Mama's soul.

131
00:11:22,510 --> 00:11:26,610
The next time you betray Mama to eat,
you won't be let off so easily!

132
00:11:26,610 --> 00:11:31,420
I'm sorry... but...
those thunderclouds were delicious!

133
00:11:31,420 --> 00:11:34,030
Are you really listening to me?!

134
00:11:34,030 --> 00:11:35,940
We can't steer the ship!

135
00:11:35,940 --> 00:11:37,410
We're going to be swept away!

136
00:11:44,590 --> 00:11:46,300
A path opened up!

137
00:11:46,300 --> 00:11:48,720
We can break through the enemy line!

138
00:11:48,720 --> 00:11:50,610
Carrot is amazing!

139
00:11:50,610 --> 00:11:54,450
Chopper! We have to protect the ship!

140
00:11:54,450 --> 00:11:55,310
Yeah!

141
00:11:58,340 --> 00:12:00,560
No, they're coming back!

142
00:12:13,220 --> 00:12:16,590
Carrot-san, wonderful!

143
00:12:16,590 --> 00:12:19,600
Hey! That skeleton's running on the sea!

144
00:12:20,190 --> 00:12:21,730
Stop him in his tracks!

145
00:12:21,730 --> 00:12:25,070
I must keep up with her, too!

146
00:12:26,000 --> 00:12:28,140
Shoot! Shoot!

147
00:12:53,860 --> 00:12:57,870
I'm starting to lose consciousness!
I'll have to stop soon.

148
00:12:57,870 --> 00:12:59,430
How many ships are left?

149
00:12:59,430 --> 00:13:01,220
Damn that little rabbit!

150
00:13:01,220 --> 00:13:03,520
Jinn-uinely Enraged Cleave!

151
00:13:05,760 --> 00:13:07,490
He saved me the work!

152
00:13:07,490 --> 00:13:09,350
We'll get her this time!

153
00:13:37,910 --> 00:13:39,080
Jinni...

154
00:13:40,160 --> 00:13:41,450
Carrot-san !

155
00:13:43,500 --> 00:13:45,330
...Shredder!

156
00:13:47,630 --> 00:13:50,590
Go to hell, brat!

157
00:13:50,590 --> 00:13:53,170
I'm sorry, Pedro...

158
00:14:06,050 --> 00:14:08,030
Baron Corpse!

159
00:14:08,030 --> 00:14:10,040
I'm glad that you're okay!

160
00:14:10,040 --> 00:14:14,440
Even though it was only a little bit of assistance...
I put one of the ships over there to sleep!

161
00:14:14,440 --> 00:14:18,020
You've already done enough.
Let's go back!

162
00:14:20,390 --> 00:14:22,920
You saved me! Thank you!

163
00:14:22,920 --> 00:14:24,400
That's our line.

164
00:14:24,400 --> 00:14:27,420
How do you turn back to normal?

165
00:14:27,420 --> 00:14:31,860
If I block my eyes
from seeing the moonlight...

166
00:14:32,600 --> 00:14:39,040
using a hat or some sunglasses...
or by simply closing my eyes...

167
00:14:39,040 --> 00:14:43,260
The moonlight from a full moon
enhances our abilities!

168
00:14:43,260 --> 00:14:46,210
That was truly beautiful!

169
00:14:50,600 --> 00:14:53,060
Carrot, are you all right?!

170
00:14:54,260 --> 00:14:55,060
Yeah...

171
00:14:55,060 --> 00:14:59,810
Thank you!
You helped us out of a big pinch!

172
00:14:59,810 --> 00:15:03,940
We were surrounded by enemies
and our ship was almost sunk!

173
00:15:05,720 --> 00:15:08,380
I'm glad I was able to help.

174
00:15:08,380 --> 00:15:12,660
Can I go into a room
where there's no moonlight?

175
00:15:13,330 --> 00:15:18,270
Of course! Leave it to us
and get some rest!

176
00:15:21,540 --> 00:15:25,190
Brother Peros!
Big Brother Daifuku can't fight anymore!

177
00:15:25,190 --> 00:15:27,380
His fleet is drifting away!

178
00:15:27,380 --> 00:15:31,290
How useless... Daifuku!

179
00:15:34,280 --> 00:15:37,550
Mama... Are you really all right?!

180
00:15:43,040 --> 00:15:44,340
There they are...

181
00:15:44,340 --> 00:15:46,310
They're coming, Mama!

182
00:15:47,890 --> 00:15:49,940
Zeus! Prometheus!

183
00:15:49,940 --> 00:15:52,480
We're on our way!

184
00:15:57,150 --> 00:15:59,370
Mama?! She looks like a different person...

185
00:15:59,370 --> 00:16:03,540
Why is she so light?!
Is it because she's so hungry?!

186
00:16:05,460 --> 00:16:11,540
Lick. How long has it been
since I saw Mama move so fast?!

187
00:16:12,410 --> 00:16:16,010
Give me the wedding cake!

188
00:16:16,010 --> 00:16:18,660
Big Mom is coming!

189
00:16:21,380 --> 00:16:23,410
Napoleon!

190
00:16:23,410 --> 00:16:25,800
Transform into a sword!

191
00:16:26,270 --> 00:16:28,180
Yes, Mama!

192
00:16:44,220 --> 00:16:46,200
What the hell is that?!

193
00:16:46,200 --> 00:16:48,240
Mama...

194
00:16:50,330 --> 00:16:53,420
Straw Hat!

195
00:17:13,560 --> 00:17:15,100
No way!

196
00:17:16,800 --> 00:17:18,700
Big Mom!

197
00:17:19,900 --> 00:17:22,170
What has she turned into?!

198
00:17:24,990 --> 00:17:28,790
Where is my wedding cake?

199
00:17:30,450 --> 00:17:35,880
Stand back, guys!
Be prepared to abandon ship!

200
00:17:36,510 --> 00:17:37,840
But...

201
00:17:39,000 --> 00:17:43,600
Oh... I'm so hungry.

202
00:17:43,600 --> 00:17:49,080
But nothing else can satisfy me.

203
00:17:49,080 --> 00:17:50,160
Where is it?!

204
00:17:53,920 --> 00:17:58,360
Where is the wedding cake?!

205
00:17:58,360 --> 00:18:00,200
No! The Sunny !

206
00:18:00,200 --> 00:18:01,450
Oh, no!

207
00:18:01,450 --> 00:18:04,910
How are we going to chase off
such a monster?!

208
00:18:13,410 --> 00:18:15,280
That scared me!

209
00:18:36,340 --> 00:18:38,010
Mirrors are...

210
00:18:38,010 --> 00:18:39,300
If this continues,

211
00:18:39,300 --> 00:18:42,030
all of the mirrors in this town will be gone!

212
00:18:42,030 --> 00:18:47,260
I didn't expect him to fight this long
against Commander Katakuri in the Mirro-world...

213
00:18:49,890 --> 00:18:53,360
We keep getting reports of mirror-breakings
from various islands.

214
00:18:53,360 --> 00:18:57,040
It's already 9:30 p.m.-soir.

215
00:18:57,040 --> 00:19:00,780
It's been almost 12 hours
since the assault on the tea party!

216
00:19:00,820 --> 00:19:03,420
What's going on? Dammit!

217
00:19:05,700 --> 00:19:10,320
Hey, everyone...
Do you wanna know something interesting?

218
00:19:10,320 --> 00:19:14,500
Hey, stop!
Their chance of survival will lower even more.

219
00:19:14,500 --> 00:19:17,340
What is it, Mistress Stussy?

220
00:19:19,460 --> 00:19:22,050
At the tea party, Linlin revealed...

221
00:19:22,630 --> 00:19:25,890
the Tamate Box from Ryugu Palace.

222
00:19:25,890 --> 00:19:27,550
She got it...

223
00:19:27,550 --> 00:19:30,640
from Straw Hat Luffy, didn't she?

224
00:19:31,550 --> 00:19:33,270
So what?

225
00:19:33,270 --> 00:19:35,360
That Tamate Box...

226
00:19:36,850 --> 00:19:39,360
contained explosives.

227
00:19:40,560 --> 00:19:42,660
Are you sure-bon ?

228
00:19:45,850 --> 00:19:49,490
Oh... he's still so perfect and cool.

229
00:19:50,940 --> 00:19:53,350
Big Brother Katakuri!

230
00:19:53,350 --> 00:19:54,370
And...

231
00:19:54,370 --> 00:19:57,010
haven't you gotten a
clear shot yet, sniper?

232
00:19:57,010 --> 00:20:01,460
Well, I've been shooting at him
without being noticed...

233
00:20:01,460 --> 00:20:05,470
but he's moving so fast!

234
00:20:05,470 --> 00:20:06,340
Damn!

235
00:20:06,340 --> 00:20:08,920
Man...! You're useless!

236
00:20:11,790 --> 00:20:13,470
This sucks!

237
00:20:13,470 --> 00:20:18,520
If we don't take out Straw Hat soon,
Big Brother Katakuri will bring him down.

238
00:20:19,590 --> 00:20:25,110
Everyone! Whose head is
going to be patted by Big Brother?!

239
00:20:25,110 --> 00:20:28,740
Of course, it's Lady Flambé's!

240
00:20:28,740 --> 00:20:30,490
I thought so!

241
00:20:37,180 --> 00:20:39,840
I have 41 older brothers.

242
00:20:39,840 --> 00:20:45,990
And 40 of them voted in the Best Little Sister Awards.

243
00:20:47,120 --> 00:20:48,920
I won!

244
00:20:48,920 --> 00:20:51,970
Everyone loves me!

245
00:20:53,080 --> 00:20:56,600
That means I'm everyone's favorite!

246
00:20:57,800 --> 00:21:00,640
I'm gonna be the king of the little sisters!

247
00:21:01,730 --> 00:21:03,600
So cute!

248
00:21:05,430 --> 00:21:09,110
Everyone wants to be
Big Brother Katakuri's favorite!

249
00:21:09,110 --> 00:21:14,890
But he's an icon for all
his 38 younger sisters!

250
00:21:14,890 --> 00:21:20,550
Even all his younger brothers admire him.
There are too many rivals!

251
00:21:21,200 --> 00:21:25,260
So I wanna help him now
to earn some bonus points!

252
00:21:25,260 --> 00:21:27,360
We know how you feel, Lady Flambé!

253
00:21:28,410 --> 00:21:31,600
We want Commander Katakuri
to like us, too!

254
00:21:31,600 --> 00:21:34,840
I don't care about you guys!

255
00:21:35,420 --> 00:21:40,190
When we got here,
he didn't seem like himself.

256
00:21:41,670 --> 00:21:44,620
But now he's as cool as always!

257
00:21:46,300 --> 00:21:50,440
Anyway, I can't stand to see him
having a hard time against an enemy.

258
00:21:53,940 --> 00:21:57,530
He should be perfect at all times...

259
00:21:57,530 --> 00:21:59,990
or I'll be disappointed!

260
00:22:01,280 --> 00:22:02,500
You're right.

261
00:22:03,240 --> 00:22:06,960
But he's not having a hard time now.

262
00:22:06,960 --> 00:22:09,610
It's just that the enemy's persistent!

263
00:22:09,610 --> 00:22:14,100
He must've received mortal wounds
dozens of times, but he keeps getting up.

264
00:22:21,100 --> 00:22:23,220
What a fool!

265
00:22:24,010 --> 00:22:26,390
How laughable.

266
00:22:45,090 --> 00:22:48,520
Wedding cake!

267
00:22:48,520 --> 00:22:52,170
Did you hide it in here?!

268
00:22:52,170 --> 00:22:54,260
Wait, Big Mom!

269
00:22:55,980 --> 00:22:57,470
I don't see it!

270
00:22:59,340 --> 00:23:02,180
It's not here!

271
00:23:02,180 --> 00:23:06,640
Stop! There's no cake on this ship!

272
00:23:08,030 --> 00:23:10,020
What?!

273
00:23:10,020 --> 00:23:13,980
Don't be ridiculous...
That can't be true!

274
00:23:15,030 --> 00:23:18,620
Because my son told me that it's here!

275
00:23:18,620 --> 00:23:24,840
If it's not here, then I'll have to take
my eldest son's life with my own hands!

276
00:23:27,260 --> 00:23:31,220
Sh-She remembers!

277
00:23:32,810 --> 00:23:35,340
If you're lying to me,

278
00:23:35,340 --> 00:23:39,300
you'll pay with your lifespan!

279
00:23:40,960 --> 00:23:46,050
Just how conscious is she right now?!

280
00:23:48,210 --> 00:23:51,280
I thought I could get away with it!

281
00:23:55,110 --> 00:24:00,730
Don't you dare call my son a liar!

282
00:24:01,500 --> 00:24:03,000
Hey, Napoleon!

283
00:24:03,000 --> 00:24:04,330
Yes, Mama!

284
00:24:05,920 --> 00:24:07,420
Let's do it.

285
00:24:11,420 --> 00:24:13,110
Cognac!

286
00:24:13,110 --> 00:24:15,910
I'll burn you and cut you in half!

287
00:24:15,910 --> 00:24:17,210
A big flaming sword!

288
00:24:17,210 --> 00:24:19,460
No chance! Get away, Jinbe!

289
00:24:19,460 --> 00:24:21,600
Go to hell!

290
00:24:23,350 --> 00:24:24,670
Shark Skin!

291
00:24:24,670 --> 00:24:26,880
Blade of Destruction!

292
00:24:37,200 --> 00:24:38,540
What in the world?!

293
00:24:38,540 --> 00:24:41,150
He stopped Cognac!

294
00:24:41,150 --> 00:24:43,310
Jinbe!

295
00:24:48,070 --> 00:24:50,660
Don't think...

296
00:24:52,820 --> 00:24:57,120
you can overpower me,
you damn shark!

297
00:25:02,170 --> 00:25:03,380
Jinbe-san !

298
00:25:03,380 --> 00:25:04,420
Oh, no!

299
00:25:04,420 --> 00:25:05,590
Jinbe!

300
00:25:14,440 --> 00:25:17,440
Where is it?! Bring out the cake!

301
00:25:17,440 --> 00:25:20,310
I'm starving to death!

302
00:25:20,320 --> 00:25:21,520
Carrot!

303
00:25:22,520 --> 00:25:24,520
Stop it, Big Mom!

304
00:25:26,320 --> 00:25:29,240
Carrot is in that room!

305
00:25:29,240 --> 00:25:32,150
If you want me to stop...

306
00:25:32,460 --> 00:25:33,450
Nami!

307
00:25:33,450 --> 00:25:35,060
Tell me where it is!

308
00:25:42,720 --> 00:25:43,510
Nami!

309
00:25:44,470 --> 00:25:45,890
I'm fine!

310
00:25:49,680 --> 00:25:54,600
Oh, no! The sail caught
fire from Big Mom's head!

311
00:25:56,580 --> 00:25:58,810
Where did you hide...

312
00:25:58,820 --> 00:26:01,050
Run, Nami!

313
00:26:01,050 --> 00:26:05,270
that massive cake?!

314
00:26:07,540 --> 00:26:09,540
Guard Point!

315
00:26:13,880 --> 00:26:15,240
Chopper!

316
00:26:16,050 --> 00:26:18,780
Well, well...

317
00:26:19,230 --> 00:26:24,670
Look what you've turned into!
They're getting more and more exotic.

318
00:26:24,670 --> 00:26:28,530
I'll definitely add you
to my collection of strange beasts!

319
00:26:28,530 --> 00:26:31,700
You chubby little tanuki...

320
00:26:31,700 --> 00:26:35,650
I'm not a tanuki ! I'm a reindeer!

321
00:26:37,900 --> 00:26:43,310
Once I get the wedding cake,
both you and Soul King will belong to me!

322
00:26:43,310 --> 00:26:48,210
Let go of me! The cake isn't here,
and I'm not your plaything!

323
00:26:48,210 --> 00:26:49,400
Chopper!

324
00:26:50,760 --> 00:26:56,340
Oh! If Mama sinks their ship,
maybe my lie will go down with it!

325
00:26:56,340 --> 00:27:01,450
If the Straw Hats lose their ship,
they'll basically be done for!

326
00:27:02,760 --> 00:27:04,370
The ship...!

327
00:27:04,370 --> 00:27:09,480
The ship's burning!

328
00:27:25,960 --> 00:27:27,760
Gum-Gum...

329
00:27:27,760 --> 00:27:30,320
Hawk Stamp!

330
00:27:41,290 --> 00:27:43,170
Did he try to dodge?

331
00:27:48,430 --> 00:27:50,260
Why won't the lights go out...

332
00:27:53,750 --> 00:27:55,510
in your...

333
00:27:57,260 --> 00:27:58,510
eyes!

334
00:28:28,870 --> 00:28:34,180
I don't understand you.
Falling down to the ground is disgraceful.

335
00:29:00,080 --> 00:29:01,690
The ship...!

336
00:29:01,690 --> 00:29:07,020
The ship is burning!

337
00:29:09,110 --> 00:29:14,530
Now, where is the wedding cake?

338
00:29:14,530 --> 00:29:15,540
Let go of me!

339
00:29:15,540 --> 00:29:16,470
Chopper!

340
00:29:16,470 --> 00:29:19,550
What should I do? What should I do?
We have to put out the fire!

341
00:29:19,550 --> 00:29:22,190
Water! Water!

342
00:29:25,850 --> 00:29:27,380
Ocean Current...

343
00:29:30,800 --> 00:29:33,890
Shoulder Throw!

344
00:30:09,140 --> 00:30:10,590
Ouch! Ow, ow, ow...

345
00:30:10,590 --> 00:30:13,470
Damn! Suddenly, the water...!

346
00:30:19,810 --> 00:30:21,630
Jinbe-san !

347
00:30:23,580 --> 00:30:25,470
Mama!

348
00:30:25,930 --> 00:30:30,470
Get off of this ship, Big Mom!

349
00:30:30,470 --> 00:30:32,460
If that's what you want...

350
00:30:34,850 --> 00:30:37,940
then hand over the cake!

351
00:30:38,980 --> 00:30:42,860
Fishman Karate Secret Technique!

352
00:30:44,990 --> 00:30:47,370
Vagabond Drill!

353
00:31:13,040 --> 00:31:14,180
Mama!

354
00:31:17,140 --> 00:31:19,270
What?!

355
00:31:21,070 --> 00:31:24,210
Yay! He kicked her out!

356
00:31:24,210 --> 00:31:26,030
Jinbe, you're amazing!

357
00:31:27,070 --> 00:31:28,200
Thank goodness!

358
00:31:28,200 --> 00:31:29,300
You did it!

359
00:31:29,300 --> 00:31:31,330
Guys!

360
00:31:31,330 --> 00:31:33,630
If we allow them
to damage the ship any further,

361
00:31:33,630 --> 00:31:36,230
how will we face Luffy and the others?!

362
00:31:36,230 --> 00:31:38,520
The ship cannot slow down!

363
00:31:38,520 --> 00:31:43,010
If Perospero and the others
catch up to us, that'll be the end of the line!

364
00:31:43,010 --> 00:31:43,650
Yeah!

365
00:31:43,650 --> 00:31:44,540
Okay!

366
00:31:44,540 --> 00:31:46,300
You can count on us!

367
00:31:47,630 --> 00:31:48,760
I'm sorry, but...

368
00:31:48,760 --> 00:31:53,470
Big Mom will regain her footing right away!

369
00:31:56,890 --> 00:31:58,040
How's Carrot?

370
00:31:58,040 --> 00:31:59,250
She's okay!

371
00:32:00,310 --> 00:32:02,810
Let's lose them at full speed!

372
00:32:07,650 --> 00:32:10,020
Mama, are you okay?

373
00:32:10,020 --> 00:32:11,240
Yeah!

374
00:32:15,200 --> 00:32:18,620
That wasn't so bad, Jinbe!

375
00:32:19,330 --> 00:32:20,410
Here she comes!

376
00:32:20,410 --> 00:32:24,380
Oh! I have an idea!

377
00:32:27,510 --> 00:32:29,430
Let's slice it up!

378
00:32:29,430 --> 00:32:31,840
That's a good idea, Mama!

379
00:32:31,840 --> 00:32:35,560
Then, I'm sure I'll find it!

380
00:32:37,520 --> 00:32:39,770
The wedding cake!

381
00:32:39,770 --> 00:32:43,400
It stretched this time!
If she swings that sword around...

382
00:32:43,400 --> 00:32:45,640
...the ship will be finished!

383
00:32:45,640 --> 00:32:48,730
At least Big Mom isn't on the ship anymore!

384
00:32:48,730 --> 00:32:50,960
All right, Zeus-chan...

385
00:32:52,370 --> 00:32:53,860
You like these, right?

386
00:32:55,280 --> 00:32:56,780
Those are...!

387
00:32:57,200 --> 00:32:58,610
Black Ball!

388
00:33:02,250 --> 00:33:06,580
It's delicious!
It's delicious! So delicious!

389
00:33:08,590 --> 00:33:11,010
Yum-yum!

390
00:33:11,010 --> 00:33:14,130
That's right! Now, help yourself!

391
00:33:14,130 --> 00:33:16,580
What should I do?!

392
00:33:16,580 --> 00:33:20,620
Humph! The same trick won't work twice!

393
00:33:23,020 --> 00:33:27,350
Don't try to fool me, you temptress!

394
00:33:27,350 --> 00:33:29,650
Nami!

395
00:33:34,280 --> 00:33:35,840
It's me.

396
00:33:35,840 --> 00:33:37,490
Oh, please!

397
00:33:43,750 --> 00:33:48,420
That's right... I don't have any flesh,
so lightning doesn't affect me.

398
00:33:49,160 --> 00:33:51,340
Oh yeah?

399
00:33:51,340 --> 00:33:55,470
Do you wanna fight me again, Soul King?!

400
00:33:55,470 --> 00:34:01,220
I remember that you couldn't even
scratch me with your sword before!

401
00:34:01,240 --> 00:34:05,840
You're right... So may I at least...

402
00:34:05,840 --> 00:34:09,940
see your panties?!

403
00:34:11,550 --> 00:34:13,760
Huh?!

404
00:34:13,760 --> 00:34:15,390
What?!

405
00:34:27,280 --> 00:34:28,610
Okay.

406
00:34:28,610 --> 00:34:31,080
It's done!

407
00:34:31,650 --> 00:34:34,570
Three-Pace Hum...

408
00:34:34,570 --> 00:34:37,160
Soul...

409
00:34:38,520 --> 00:34:40,290
Notch Slash!

410
00:34:43,680 --> 00:34:48,590
From the very beginning,
our target was you alone, Zeus!

411
00:34:48,590 --> 00:34:51,930
Ow, ow, ow! Damn!
I let my guard down!

412
00:34:51,930 --> 00:34:53,970
Stay with us, Zeus!

413
00:34:58,390 --> 00:35:01,310
Positive Charge Black Ball!

414
00:35:01,310 --> 00:35:05,480
Discharge and feel better, Zeus-chan !

415
00:35:05,480 --> 00:35:07,280
You...!

416
00:35:09,030 --> 00:35:11,740
Th-This is...

417
00:35:13,780 --> 00:35:14,900
What is it?!

418
00:35:28,880 --> 00:35:30,310
Mama!

419
00:35:30,850 --> 00:35:32,670
You're kidding me, Mama!

420
00:35:32,670 --> 00:35:34,570
Zeus discharged!

421
00:35:37,900 --> 00:35:39,500
Mama!

422
00:35:40,820 --> 00:35:42,120
We did it!

423
00:35:42,120 --> 00:35:46,840
We bought some time!
Let's make some headway now!

424
00:35:46,840 --> 00:35:48,550
Hurry up, Brook!

425
00:35:48,550 --> 00:35:49,590
Okay!

426
00:35:52,870 --> 00:35:54,260
Grab this!

427
00:35:59,340 --> 00:36:01,140
I'm back!

428
00:36:01,140 --> 00:36:03,290
Yay! Welcome back!

429
00:36:03,290 --> 00:36:05,220
Brook, well done!

430
00:36:06,600 --> 00:36:12,780
We tried to minimize the damage,
but it's quite bad.

431
00:36:14,060 --> 00:36:15,820
Oh, yeah.

432
00:36:15,820 --> 00:36:17,820
I brought something back.

433
00:36:19,370 --> 00:36:20,920
Oh, Zeus!

434
00:36:20,920 --> 00:36:23,200
I-Isn't he dangerous?

435
00:36:23,200 --> 00:36:25,700
I don't think he has much energy left...

436
00:36:27,900 --> 00:36:30,080
Oh, where am I?

437
00:36:31,950 --> 00:36:34,290
Nice to see you again, Zeus.

438
00:36:35,820 --> 00:36:38,100
Nice... to... see you... too...

439
00:36:40,790 --> 00:36:45,230
As I recall, you tried to...

440
00:36:45,230 --> 00:36:49,800
strike me with lightning earlier.

441
00:36:49,800 --> 00:36:50,640
I'm sorry...

442
00:36:50,640 --> 00:36:55,390
If "sorry" were enough,
there would be no need for sheriffs or the Navy.

443
00:36:59,300 --> 00:37:02,270
I bet you got the wrong idea earlier...

444
00:37:02,270 --> 00:37:08,280
I didn't ask you to be my friend...

445
00:37:08,280 --> 00:37:09,140
What?

446
00:37:09,140 --> 00:37:11,030
I'll ask you one more time...

447
00:37:12,170 --> 00:37:15,870
Will you be my servant...
or would you rather...

448
00:37:17,100 --> 00:37:18,370
die?

449
00:37:19,580 --> 00:37:22,990
Think about it carefully.

450
00:37:26,210 --> 00:37:30,010
Mama! Mama!

451
00:37:31,810 --> 00:37:33,720
Shut up...

452
00:37:33,720 --> 00:37:35,060
Mama!

453
00:37:37,590 --> 00:37:39,930
Chase them, Prometheus!

454
00:37:39,930 --> 00:37:41,550
Yes, Mama!

